data.description: Great opportunity in this highly desirable neighborhood adjacent to Western Golf & Country Club. Spacious Brick Bungalow featuring 3 bedrooms (including a first floor primary w/ dual closets), 2 full baths, nice sized living room with a wood-burning fireplace, dining room, 2 1/2 car garage and a great lot. Flex room upstairs is ideal as an office or a 4th bedroom. Hardwood floors on the main floor under carpeting. Furnace & A/C within past 5 years, Roof (2016). Price reflects updates needed and would be ideal for an investor or a home buyer looking to build sweat equity. Estate sale. Home is being Sold As-Is. BATVAI - Buyer/ Buyer’s Agent to Verify All Information. Sale is subject to Probate Court Approval.
